      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Requires Wave 2 — Chat telemetry to InfluxDB\n\nOpen WebUI does not expose a Prometheus endpoint and stores conversation state in **SQLite inside the container**. Wave 2 adds a poller (`files/openwebui/exporter.py`) that reads `webui.db` and writes to InfluxDB. Until then this dashboard shows **nginx upstream metrics** (real), **container resources** (real), and **placeholder stat tiles** for chat counters."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Conversations today (placeholder — Wave 2)",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 4},
      "targets": [{"refId": "A", "expr": "vector(0)", "legendFormat": "placeholder"}],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}, "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "blue", "value": null}]}, "noValue": "Wave 2"}, "overrides": []},
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "textMode": "auto", "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "none"}
    },
